flowchart TD
    A([Upload\nfile_old + file_new + parser_type]) --> B[Extractor\npdfplumber_extractor\nPageText per page]

    B --> C[Parser]
    C --> FD[fd_parser\nFise de Disciplina\nSections: Identificare, Obiective,\nCompetente, Continuturi,\nStructura, Evaluare, Bibliografie]
    C --> PI[pi_parser\nPlanuri de Invatamant\nALL-CAPS lines as section headers]

    FD --> D[Differ\ndifflib_differ\nline-level diffs per section]
    PI --> D

    D --> E[Analyzer\nregex_analyzer\ndetect semantic changes]

    E --> F([DiffResponse])

    F --> G[sections: SectionDiff\nequal - modified - added - removed\nwith inline word-level diffs]
    F --> H[logic_changes: LogicChange\nHOURS_CHANGED, ECTS_CHANGED\nwith severity levels]
    F --> I[summary: DiffSummary\ntotal_sections + modified\nadded + removed + unchanged]
